-meta\">\n   335→                    <a href=\"https://github.com/continuedev/continue/releases/tag/v1.5.45\" target=\"_blank\">View Release</a>\n   336→                    <span class=\"source-link\">2026-03-04</span>\n   337→                </div>\n   338→            </div>\n   339→\n   340→            <div class=\"item\">\n   341→                <div class=\"item-title\">\n   342→                    <span class=\"product-name\">Aider</span>\n   343→                    <span class=\"update-badge feature\">feature</span>\n   344→                </div>\n   345→                <div class=\"item-description\">\n   346→                    Added overeager: true setting to gpt-5.2-codex model variants and gpt-4-turbo. Enhanced overeager prompt functionality in ask_prompts.py for more proactive AI responses.\n   347→                </div>\n   348→                <div class=\"item-meta\">\n   349→                    <a href=\"https://github.com/Aider-AI/aider/commits/main\" target=\"_blank\">View Details</a>\n   350→                    <span class=\"source-link\">2026-03-03</span>\n   351→                </div>\n   352→            </div>\n   353→\n   354→            <div class=\"item\">\n   355→                <div class=\"item-title\">\n   356→                    <span class=\"product-name\">Continue</span>\n   357→                    <span class=\"update-badge release\">release</span>\n   358→                    v1.5.44\n   359→                </div>\n   360→                <div class=\"item-description\">\n   361→                    Version 1.5.44 release built and published from the main branch.\n   362→                </div>\n   363→                <div class=\"item-meta\">\n   364→                    <a href=\"https://github.com/continuedev/continue/releases/tag/v1.5.44\" target=\"_blank\">View Release</a>\n   365→                    <span class=\"source-link\">2026-03-02</span>\n   366→                </div>\n   367→            </div>\n   368→\n   369→            <d