 class=\"item\">\n   492→                <div class=\"item-title\">\n   493→                    <a href=\"https://github.com/jnemargut/better-plan-mode\" target=\"_blank\">Show HN: A Claude Code skill that renders decisions as interactive HTML pages</a>\n   494→                </div>\n   495→                <div class=\"item-description\">\n   496→                    A new tool for Claude Code that visualizes AI decision-making processes as interactive HTML pages, improving transparency and understanding of AI reasoning.\n   497→                </div>\n   498→                <div class=\"item-meta\">\n   499→                    <span class=\"tag\">Claude</span>\n   500→                    <span class=\"tag\">AI</span>\n   501→                    <span class=\"tag\">visualization</span>\n   502→                    <a href=\"https://news.ycombinator.com/user?id=jontomato\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"source-link\">jontomato</a>\n   503→                </div>\n   504→            </div>\n   505→\n   506→            <div class=\"item\">\n   507→                <div class=\"item-title\">\n   508→                    <a href=\"https://www.palkeo.com/en/blog/foreman.html\" target=\"_blank\">Foreman: A secure self-hosted agent orchestrator</a>\n   509→                </div>\n   510→                <div class=\"item-description\">\n   511→                    Release of Foreman, a self-hosted tool for orchestrating AI agents with a focus on security and local deployment options for AI-powered workflows.\n   512→                </div>\n   513→                <div class=\"item-meta\">\n   514→                    <span class=\"tag\">AI</span>\n   515→                    <span class=\"tag\">agents</span>\n   516→                    <span class=\"tag\">orchestration</span>\n   517→                    <a href=\"https://news.ycombinator.com/user?id=palkeo\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"source-link\">palkeo</a>\n   518→                </div>\n   519→            </div>\n   520→\n   521→     